  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505146758\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sKhau2Mo5bxefgAHZRib5BvXxT21QiaM5vZIUiaO3ia33KaPgk2woiaQto3Q/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f5414634&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sKhau2Mo5bxefgAHZRib5BvXxT21QiaM5vZIUiaO3ia33KaPgk2woiaQto3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">90%的开发者都在用AI，却只有24%真正信任它！DORA 2025报告揭示：AI不是万能解药，而是放大镜。它让强者飞升，让弱者溃败。七种团队人设、七项关键能力，决定了你的团队，是进化还是崩塌。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">十年来，Google Cloud的DORA报告一直被视为观察全球软件团队的风向标。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而2025年这份新报告，把焦点放在了一个前所未有的主题上——AI已经全面渗透开发流程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"725\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"735\" data-imgfileid=\"505146529\" data-ratio=\"1.2894736842105263\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"570\" data-width=\"570\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6af17f5d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sicnibjxrQxo3LwrnhvIFxEq2esVarwrwYD8suqIOm78yCiahNJZ4icgrrQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">近五千名技术从业者的调研结果表明，AI不再是尝鲜，而是主流。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">开发者用它写代码、改 bug、补文档，甚至参与产品决策。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它既像「镜子」，折射出团队的真实状态，也像「放大器」，让优势和短板同时被放大。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可最诡异的是：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当90%的人都在用</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">时，真正信任它的人却寥寥无几。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI成为标配，却没人真信？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据报告显示，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">高达90%的开发者已经在日常工作中使用</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，这一比例比去年上涨了14%</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们也不再是偶尔使用AI，而是达到</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">每天中位数两小时</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，约占工作日的四分之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种「深度绑定」几乎覆盖了开发流程的各个环节。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">写新代码（71%）、修改已有代码（66%）、写文档（64%）、创建测试用例（62%）等都已成为AI的主战场。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"316\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"474\" data-imgfileid=\"505146520\" data-ratio=\"0.5622775800711743\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"843\" data-width=\"843\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1e08fc85&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sUAbISZedAiaE9K1MonGBsmVTXW3egaLZ9XRpZ3NcmCaKj2rmd2eEvlQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">开发者在不同任务中使用AI的比例。写新代码、改bug和写文档是最常见的应用场景</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而且，绝大多数人都感受到了回报：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">80%的人认为生产力显著提升，59%的人表示代码质量更好</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"331\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"488\" data-imgfileid=\"505146528\" data-ratio=\"0.5886610373944512\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"829\" data-width=\"829\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4ef8dedf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sXMjx1PyJUKePIAY3ed5xvIeGx2SHwuXyfOicXFHUvxkhpibiaEP0VURBw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一位受访开发者甚至说：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI有时写出的代码比我更好，因为它往往更整洁，符合标准，而我可能会偷懒忘记重构。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，数据背后却隐藏着一个惊人的反差。</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">明明人人在用，却几乎没人真信。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">调查显示，虽然七成开发者对AI输出有一定程度的信心，但只有24%的人表示「高度信任」，其中仅4%「非常信任」，20%「比较信任」，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">仍有30%的人几乎不信任。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"271\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"414\" data-imgfileid=\"505146518\" data-ratio=\"0.4813953488372093\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"860\" data-width=\"860\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71a8a3e8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0smibMHOOaurHh8JMgev5UGPb8IV7zsdOFw8CDgBHxVDAd88GVqLbQpgA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">开发者对AI输出结果的信任分布</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究团队把这种现象称作</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">「信任悖论」</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：AI已成为写代码、调bug的标配工具，但人们对它的信任却并未同步增长。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种心理有点类似Stack Overflow ——开发者天天用，但始终保持着一丝怀疑态度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这也表明了，AI已经走上舞台中央，但它仍然是一位「不被完全信任的合作者」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI不是解药，而是放大镜</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果说「信任悖论」示了开发者的心理矛盾，那么另一个发现更耐人寻味：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI并不是单向的效率药丸，而是一面镜子，照出了团队真实的底色。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在那些文化健康、协作顺畅的团队里，AI的加入就像加速器，让他们的迭代更快、质量更高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但一旦环境本身存在裂缝，比如遗留系统拖累、流程僵化、沟通混乱，AI并不会救场，反而会把这些问题放大，让交付变得更加不稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">数据已经印证了这一点：个体效率、代码质量和组织绩效显著提升的同时，交付的不确定性和团队内的摩擦也在上升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"255\" data-backw=\"529\" data-height=\"255\" data-imgfileid=\"505146519\" data-ratio=\"0.4820415879017013\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"529\" data-width=\"529\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7e5997dc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sdkoqMdMJU7vHfgffJaGRdf41Jh8Q4PkvbmCMba3aSBZSXjrJ2vyVHQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">AI对个人、团队和组织的综合影响。整体表现正向，但也可能带来交付不稳定和额外摩擦</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从数据上看，个体效率、代码质量和组织绩效显著提升，但与此同时，「软件交付不稳定性」也随之上升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">部分团队的burnout和friction水平被推高。AI不会自动解决问题，只会让现状更加极端。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">报告还特别指出了一点：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">的使用与交付</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">吞吐量</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">呈正相关，这意味着高效团队正在更快发布软件</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，这也是对去年的研究结论的一次反转。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2024年的DORA报告曾发现，AI的引入和交付速度没有显著关系，而2025年的数据首次证实了它确实能让强者更强。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更有意思的是，研究者在团队访谈中发现了一种「镜像效应」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在「高效能团队」里，AI帮助他们更快完成代码审查、测试和部署，成员普遍觉得：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有了AI，大家更敢于尝试新的工作方式。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在「低效能团队」里，AI被当作「临时补丁」使用，结果bug倍增，返工频繁，团队成员甚至觉得AI「让混乱更显眼」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"337\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"720\" data-imgfileid=\"505146524\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1200\" data-width=\"1200\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f61a1973&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sqSkODjQVk1I5l7azcZcnZA933bwQibMGvViaDKVVF5ALiaH2JIoZjH9rQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了揭示背后的规律，今年的DORA报告提出了一个有趣的框架：七种典型的团队「人设」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有些团队被称为「和谐高绩效」，因为他们能用AI放大优势；有些则被归为「遗留瓶颈」，AI只会让老问题更突出；还有的则陷入「混乱拼凑」，AI反而成了新的负担。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">听上去像是一份职场MBTI测试，但背后却是对近五千个团队的系统分析。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它们共同揭示了一个事实：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">的价值，不在于有没有用，而在于你是否有能力用好它。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">七种团队人设</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI让好团队飞升，烂团队更烂</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在今年的DORA报告里，研究者把近五千个团队的画像汇总成了七种「典型人设」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"414\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"825\" data-imgfileid=\"505146525\" data-ratio=\"0.7366071428571429\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1120\" data-width=\"1120\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a9e77680&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sm44VyFITxiaVhdJ1T2ZibhewpIPTReib8odB5smgwHzI1AhibKXpjwkp6g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">七类典型研发团队的综合表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不同人设在效率、质量、交付稳定性等维度上的差异一目了然。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">「和谐高绩效团队」是人人向往的理想型。他们像一支默契的乐队，AI的介入让节奏更快、旋律更稳。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">报告显示，这类团队在几乎所有指标上都是正向加分，从效率到幸福感都位居前列。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"271\" data-backw=\"354\" data-height=\"271\" data-imgfileid=\"505146523\" data-ratio=\"0.7655367231638418\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"354\" data-width=\"354\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5d63001c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sKDdnLibFhp3rtKA45bHPVdHkjvxDCvSPeUbdA7nW28ibqMhnBbYdd2pw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与之相对的，是「遗留瓶颈团队」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们背着庞大的旧系统和僵化流程，就像一辆发动机老旧的车，即使装上最新的AI涡轮，跑起来依旧卡顿。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"343\" data-backw=\"350\" data-height=\"343\" data-imgfileid=\"505146521\" data-ratio=\"0.98\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"350\" data-width=\"350\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b4e8510c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sSF59gf7Dq8sTNCU0Jsw2PmBVelrtZDJIXKnqjW8BicxEZHtZKMl3nGQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这类团队的「交付不稳定性」指数显著飙升，AI反而成了放大镜，让缺陷更难忽视。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">还有一些处于中间地带的，比如「低频高效团队」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505146522\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.873900293255132\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"341\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"341\" data-height=\"298\" data-backw=\"341\" data-backh=\"298\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6e3c0853&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sia5SYrVIpehLEz2dyRkxB02ggnmBAoVLQofzLFltbdp0Z1iaZxjJQYLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们谨慎、慢热，但关键时刻能打出高质量的成果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI对他们而言，更像是一种「精修工具」，帮他们保持高水准，却无法解决节奏缓慢的问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这七种人设中，有的代表了未来，也有的预示了风险。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"307\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"455\" data-imgfileid=\"505146527\" data-ratio=\"0.5455635491606715\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"834\" data-width=\"834\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c1ca411b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sjBKibSejCeK7ayhoN6uuyGSRc2Zf3Hs2KkY6fQn3lF0DjFNxb40KwdA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">不同团队人设在样本中的分布。说明大多数团队仍处在「中间状态」，既有优势也存在隐患</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这就像一次「团队体检」：AI不会改变你的本质，只会让优点更亮、缺点更痛。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">至于你的团队属于哪一类，答案可能比你想象的更直白。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI生存蓝图</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">决定团队命运的七项能力</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果说「团队人设」像是一份诊断报告，告诉你你是谁，那么DORA提出的</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">能力模型</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，就是一份行动指南，告诉你该怎么做。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究者发现，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">能否真正发挥作用，不取决于有没有用，而取决于组织是否准备好承接它</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">于是，他们在今年的报告中首次提出了</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">DORA&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;Capabilities Model</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：七项关键能力，决定了一个团队能否从「遗留瓶颈」进化为「和谐高效」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"319\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"567\" data-imgfileid=\"505146526\" data-ratio=\"0.567\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1000\" data-width=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=230af298&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3b79rm7kpA34wdkflBkE0sgxgrt5hicJ6ettl3I5PngiaTBRmDqFbK3rjCAxVfDcThNdsrpssMTbibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些能力既包括技术建设，也涉及文化与制度：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">用户导向（User-Centric Focus）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：AI能否真正服务业务与用户，而不是为了炫技。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">版本控制（Strong Version Control Practice）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：是否有规范的迭代管理，避免AI引入混乱。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">数据可用性（AI-Accessible Internal Data）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：内部数据是否结构化、可被模型利用。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">小批量工作（Working in Small Batches）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：敢不敢拆解任务，让AI参与更高效的微循环。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">清晰</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">立场（Clear and Communicated AI Stance）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：组织是否明确了对AI的态度与准则。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">内部平台（Quality Internal Platform）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：有没有配套的开发平台，把AI嵌入日常流程。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">健康</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">数据生态（Healthy Data Ecosystem）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：数据治理是否到位，隐私与合规有没有保障。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些要素和最终绩效直接挂钩：版本控制与代码质量强相关，用户导向能显著提升团队表现，健康的数据生态决定组织能否长期跑下去。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">换句话说，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;成功的关键不在「买了什么工具」，而在「是否具备这七项能力」</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这也解释了为什么同样是90%的使用率，有的团队飞升，有的却陷入困境。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">DORA报告的结论很直白：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">真正成功的组织，不是先有AI才升级文化，而是先塑造文化，AI才能发挥作用。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，未来几年里，AI在开发领域的最大挑战，可能不再是技术本身，而是组织是否愿意改变。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI已经从尝鲜工具变成开发者的标配。它让效率和质量得到提升，却也可能放大组织的混乱与不稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">真正的挑战从来不是要不要用，而是团队是否具备承接它的文化与能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">DORA报告提醒我们：AI不是终点，而是一面镜子。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你的团队，会借助它飞升，还是被照出裂缝？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/developers/dora-report-2025/\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.google/technology/developers/dora-report-2025/</a></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://services.google.com/fh/files/misc/2025_state_of_ai_assisted_software_development.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://services.google.com/fh/files/misc/2025_state_of_ai_assisted_software_development.pdf</a></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌 DORA 2025 报告揭示 90%开发者日常使用 AI，但信任度低，AI 是团队效能的放大镜，并提出七项关键能力决定 AI 成功。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌 DORA 2025 报告揭示 90%开发者日常使用 AI，但信任度低，AI 是团队效能的放大镜，并提出七项关键能力决定 AI 成功。",
  "summary": "文章深入解读了 Google Cloud 发布的 DORA 2025 报告核心发现。报告指出，高达 90%的开发者已将 AI 深度融入日常工作，平均每天使用 AI 超过 2 小时，覆盖代码编写、修改、文档和测试等多个环节。然而，尽管 80%的用户感受到生产力提升，但仅 24%的开发者对 AI 输出结果表示高度信任，形成了“信任悖论”。更重要的是，报告强调 AI 并非万能解药，而是团队效能的“放大镜”：它能加速高效团队的迭代和质量，但对存在技术债务、流程僵化等问题的团队，反而会放大其短板，导致交付不稳定，并可能推高团队的倦怠感和内部摩擦。文章还介绍了 DORA 首次提出的 AI 能力模型，包含用户导向、版本控制、数据可用性等七项关键能力，强调组织文化和准备程度是 AI 能否成功的核心。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "90%开发者已日常使用 AI，但普遍缺乏高度信任。",
      "explanation": "报告显示，AI 已深度融入开发流程，但仅 24%的开发者表示高度信任，形成“信任悖论”，表明 AI 仍是“不被完全信任的合作者”。"
